creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of National Geographic Magazine Vol. 02 No. 1-2 by Various.

Read in English by Availle; Larry Wilson; Ric F; Pooja DSr; Lucretia B.; Rapunzelina; Greg Giordano
National Geographic Magazine Volume 2 Number 1: On the Telegraphic Determinations of Longitude by the Bureau of Navigation Report: Geography of the Land Report: Geography of the Air April 1890.
National Geographic Magazine Volume 2 Number 2: The Rivers of Northern New Jersey, with notes on the classification of rivers in general. A Critical Review of Bering's First Expedition, 1725-30, together with a translation of his original Report upon it. Supplementary note on the alleged observation of a Lunar Eclipse by Bering in 1728-9. May 1890.
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Standard or slim CD Case Insert available for this recording.
